Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big sale, big sale! Today we got a sweet bargain on our candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get whatever candy you want half price!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.82,0:00:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Flaky-licious" lolipop and...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.07,0:00:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,..."Fluffy-Fluffy Chocolate Takoyaki", soy sauce flavored.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.78,0:00:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All conversely the genuine article.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.82,0:00:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And half price to boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be contrarily cautious, people!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Coz this candy here has a hidden flip side!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.54,0:00:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something he's not telling us?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.75,0:00:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn brat! You tryin' to nitpick inside my shop?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is what you're saying true, contrarily?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.38,0:00:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This world is filled with hidden truths.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.43,0:00:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel with me and conversely prove yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.68,0:00:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's reverse!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.85,0:00:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Permanent Trap, Uratra C!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contractivate!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That card...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.39,0:00:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I reversely Special Summon Gurensaurus!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Learned a lesson, on the contrary?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.87,0:01:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how backwards society is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.20,0:01:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As we contrarily agreed, I'll be taking this with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.92,0:01:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything has an opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.88,0:01:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Candy sold at half price, for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whether your mother's in a good mood,\N or there's no homework...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.22,0:01:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I keep telling you, It's true-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.68,0:01:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upside down..?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.14,0:01:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.21,0:01:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything, without a doubt, has a hidden flipside, inversely.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.28,0:01:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Clean up! Clean up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.48,0:01:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Naturally, this guy has a flipside, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Upside down! Upside down!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.82,0:01:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, the most suspicious of them all currently is... that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma Tsukumo, contrarily!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.83,0:01:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I completely forgot about that errand Sis asked for!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.44,0:01:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.53,0:01:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yuma Tsukumo, a guy famous for such weak Dueling skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.72,0:02:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's hard to believe he manage to beat Shark, who won the national championships.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.00,0:02:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's definitely something underneath all this, conversely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.81,0:02:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no doubt he got his hands on some questionably good cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And if I am to obtain that card for myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I gotta give him this and challenge him to a Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.52,0:02:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.41,0:02:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what this guy wants to be called.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.29,0:02:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy... here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you guys always calling him a ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I am not a ghost".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.45,0:02:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I am Astral, who came from the Astral World."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.94,0:02:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is, arguably.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's been really bossy and annoying since yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not "This guy". I'm Astral.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah--! I got it already...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's even got a name now..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These symptoms are pretty serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.34,0:02:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.05,0:02:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why if it isn't Yuma-{\i1}kun{\i0}, conversely!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.12,0:02:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokunosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.60,0:02:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys chatting about so inversely happily?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.89,0:02:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything bad about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.89,0:02:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't mind it either way, on the contrary!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.36,0:03:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether good or bad, I welcome it all contrarily!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.65,0:03:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This boy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm pretty sure he's the one from yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you, anyways?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.45,0:03:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't heard about me, conversely?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.85,0:03:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the outside, he's just a middle school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the inside, he's just a middle school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.98,0:03:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both my inner and outter! I've achieved... inner-outer harmony!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.71,0:03:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they are talking about... Tokunosuke Omoteura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm from your neighboring class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.77,0:03:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I was thinking giving this to you, Yuma-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.74,0:03:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baby Tragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An Exceed Monster, arguably!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exceed monster!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is to thank you for conversely defeating Shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.00,0:03:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always suffered contrarily a lot thanks to that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.39,0:03:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a proof to our friendship..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.71,0:03:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Proof of our friendship, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.23,0:03:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really okay for me to take this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.39,0:03:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's something bizarre overflowing from his body...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.24,0:03:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to to be so questionably polite.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on and take it, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:04:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, then don't mind me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.33,0:04:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn to water the flowers today, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.07,0:04:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't hurry up, you won't make it on time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.02,0:04:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, but the card!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.41,0:04:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just accept Tokunosuke's card like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were in the same class as him in Elementary School, so we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy's action always has some hidden motives.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hidden?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.11,0:04:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't look like that kind of person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.28,0:04:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tch, some obstacles have contradictorily appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.11,0:04:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, I won't just give up contrarily like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.07,0:04:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will be sure to inversely hand him this card.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.74,0:04:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whether it's rainy, or windy,\N or a cold winter blizzard, or the burning sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}they're all ingredients to color each day. \NDon't lose heart, will or love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.98,0:04:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The kindness you gave me was strict,\N when we clashed I learned irritation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.05,0:04:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It starts by recognizing our differences, dancing freely,\N the creation of Heaven and Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:05:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The truth is, I was lonely. Until I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I lied to myself that being alone was easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My favorite books and hobbies,\N they don't seem to match.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You were the only one to nod in agreement with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.85,0:05:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Happiness and sadness and anger and\N Do and Re and Mi and Fa and So and La and Ti and Do,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It doesn't work unless they're different,\N the harmony and the scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.39,0:05:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No one is exactly the same,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.69,0:05:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}because that's the reason for living.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.73,0:05:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if the sounds are dissonant from time to time,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,0:05:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}don't give up on the strength that will get you through.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When we reach the edge of the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the view we see will be the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whether it's rainy, or windy,\N or a cold winter blizzard, or the burning sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're all ingredients to color each day.\N Don't lose heart, will or love.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the kindness you gave me was strict,\N when we clashed I learned irritation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.62,0:06:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It starts by recognizing our differences, dancing freely,\N the creation of Heaven and Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.32,0:06:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given this example, what do you think the correct answer is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.94,0:06:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(410,566)}"Numbers 5:\N Read the Flip Side of the Duel, Conversely"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.51,0:06:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This gigantic structure is split into several areas, that I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But what for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And also, that boy from a while ago..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.01,0:06:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The card.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.41,0:07:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HEY!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.03,0:07:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.44,0:07:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're leaving yourself wide open..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you guys being a little too distrusting?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got total protection, or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way Yuma won't be able to take the card, conversely...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's all the the Exceed Monsters? Nothing on the floor here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That guy is Yuma's classmate, Taichi..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can use this guy... or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh--? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.05,0:07:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go, I'll go, I'll go for sure--!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.67,0:07:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.43,0:07:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Both the idiot and my bait are ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.44,0:07:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Taichi phase, complete success! ...Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.92,0:07:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:07:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.80,0:08:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't go out and play Duel Monsters, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.19,0:08:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, I-I never did anything like that..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To King of Duels, Yuma-{\i1}sama{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From Yuma-{\i1}sama{\i0}'s big fan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh-! You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fan letter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.25,0:08:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, I already told him like that no Duels of any sort allowed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew about this Granny, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Yuma, those Duels are by no means just regular Duels, that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you go off to anyways?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.31,0:08:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about that! Isn't this amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.02,0:08:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a fan letter! A fan letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.31,0:08:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.68,0:08:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"What kind of effect does a fan letter have?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.22,0:08:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you gonna ask something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.11,0:08:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fan letter is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm your fan! I love you so much!"- a letter like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.15,0:08:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are forbidden from Dueling?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.00,0:08:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that, the fan letter! Fan letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.51,0:09:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Observation number eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.57,0:09:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yuma is forbidden from Dueling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.07,0:09:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.15,0:09:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... the card that Tokunosuke wanted to give me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.04,0:09:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Baby Tragon card!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.25,0:09:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote this for you with all my feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please use this card...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh-- So it was just a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I got an Exceed Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.28,0:09:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second phase, arguably a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Afterwards, it'll be the last of the finishing touches, or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.27,0:09:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just paste this here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be Yuma's debatable end...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll soon learn the dark side of the world, or will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good~ Morn~ ing~!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.35,0:09:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.93,0:09:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think of you as that type of person,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:09:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't believe you're doing this behind our backs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behind your back? Am I up to anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.63,0:10:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you up to anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.18,0:10:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even being shameless has its boundaries!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's got these anonymous photo on their mobiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.74,0:10:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To summarize, we know what you've been up to!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.26,0:10:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroying the flowerbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Causing trouble for our teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheating on your tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.31,0:10:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, you even ate Taichi's lunch,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.75,0:10:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then replaced it with a frog!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.09,0:10:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Taichi noticed this, he took the day off from school!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.51,0:10:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh--?! That Taichi was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tch! I would never do anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.45,0:10:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly what I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's gotta be a misunderstanding here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.46,0:10:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma isn't a shady guy on the inside at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two, although I can understand that you want to support Yuma-{\i1}kun{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's some reaaally solid evidence here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.71,0:10:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma-{\i1}kun{\i0}, from now on we're strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, everyone, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.76,0:10:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah--! W-wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.06,0:10:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By associating yourselves with Yuma-{\i1}kun{\i0}, nothing good will come from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, it wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.81,0:11:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The plan was a complete contradicting success!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tch..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.72,0:11:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't anyone around here to Duel with either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.54,0:11:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do things end up like this? I don't get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.02,0:11:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do any of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of effect is a "hidden side"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hidden side?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.22,0:11:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like the reason you were despised, was due to that effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.24,0:11:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hidden side" means,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.48,0:11:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you believe in your heart and what you say are totally different things, that's what it's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.73,0:11:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Totally different things...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.23,0:11:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans have a special trait like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.41,0:11:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every human has this, no matter who they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.44,0:11:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, Yuma... Why don't you have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.72,0:11:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do too! My hidden side..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.57,0:11:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing at a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.13,0:11:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokunosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.45,0:12:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what happened, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They totally ignored me. As expected, I'm pretty down...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However Yuma-{\i1}kun{\i0}, I believe in you, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I saw it. That Duel between Shark and yourself, or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.55,0:12:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything became clear from watching the Duel, or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.16,0:12:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokunosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.08,0:12:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The card you beat Shark with, what was it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aspiring Emperor - Hope, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.33,0:12:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, that's the one, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.95,0:12:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aspiring Emperor - Hope, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.30,0:12:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His bizarre energy is becoming stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.71,0:12:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is going on with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer up, or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.83,0:12:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't matter what everyone else says, I'm still on your side, conversely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.41,0:12:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just what in the world is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.17,0:12:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokunosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.46,0:12:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're actually a really awesome guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.43,0:12:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, wanna Duel, or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.72,0:12:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At times like this, it's good to have a Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.14,0:12:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Duel will surely freshen you up, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.38,0:13:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Then let's Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.45,0:13:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What an idiot, conversely taking my bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With this, Aspiring Emperor Hope will become mine, maybe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.85,0:13:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suggest avoiding Dueling against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.04,0:13:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a bad feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.42,0:13:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that you're also doubting Tokunosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.47,0:13:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.97,0:13:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokunosuke was encouraging me this whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.49,0:13:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, talking all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-nothing at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.52,0:13:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry up and duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.34,0:13:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna bring it to 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Gazer, set!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.47,0:13:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Target, lock on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.32,0:13:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}AR Vision, link complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.12,0:13:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take the first turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.99,0:13:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one Monster in face-down Defense Position.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.23,0:14:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're hardening your defense, Tokunosuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.55,0:14:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're the one that defeated that Shark, Yuma-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.39,0:14:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma. For this duel, you should also be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.79,0:14:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.02,0:14:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.06,0:14:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again, talking to himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that some kind of strategy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Face down defense monster... You won't know its Defense Power if you don't attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, if attacking unwisely, when the Defense Power is higher than the Attack Power of my monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.31,0:14:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that moment, I'll end up taking damage equal to that amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.92,0:14:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.25,0:14:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn !
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just summon a monster with higher attack power!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.76,0:14:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.55,0:14:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon Gagaga Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gagaga Magician, attack that face-down defense monster!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.96,0:14:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a light and hasty attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:14:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harisenbone, Appear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.44,0:15:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Defense point 400!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.41,0:15:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Gagaga Magician's victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flip effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.94,0:15:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flip effect?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When a flip effect monster is set face-down in defense position, the monster's flip effect will activate when flipped faced up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flip effect activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.95,0:15:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You take 400 points of damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.50,0:15:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad at all..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.75,0:15:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, it's Gagaga that has the higher attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.87,0:15:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Victory is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.36,0:15:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.44,0:15:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a weakling!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.22,0:15:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.18,0:15:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of Yuma-kun, won't be easily knocked down like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.05,0:15:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to hurt Yuma's life points!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.60,0:15:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokunosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's using flip effect monsters, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.70,0:15:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.05,0:16:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Taichi-kun's mother said that he went to school as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, just what does all of this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be, a hint to everyone's anonymous photographs...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.42,0:16:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.16,0:16:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, those photos!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.03,0:16:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this can prove Yuma's innocence..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.15,0:16:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.32,0:16:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.86,0:16:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a defense position monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another face-down defending monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.45,0:16:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going after another flip effect?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.84,0:16:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I set two cards face down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.87,0:16:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's able to read Yuma's attacks..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he aiming for...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.44,0:16:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.61,0:16:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn !!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw !!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.96,0:16:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I summon Full Elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.26,0:16:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll attack the face down defense position monster with Full Elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.43,0:16:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That face down monster, you can't attack it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.02,0:16:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.98,0:16:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I take damage or suffer from the flip effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.53,0:17:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Full Elf defeats his face down monster, Gagaga Magician will be able to attack directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.15,0:17:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Full Elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.11,0:17:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack the face down defense position monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.47,0:17:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it would come to this..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.13,0:17:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chuubone, appear!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Defense point 300!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.81,0:17:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! This one is also defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flip effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.76,0:17:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From my deck, I can special summon 3 Chuubone Juniors in defense position to my opponent's field!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.62,0:17:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh--? They're summoned to my field?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.17,0:17:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I special summoned successfully!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.09,0:17:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokunosuke..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's really no point summoning monsters to my field...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.20,0:17:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh no! I got the effect all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.37,0:17:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah--! I tend to do that a lot too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.41,0:17:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. I totally understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.03,0:18:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is a duel. I won't hold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.80,0:18:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use Gagaga Magician to attack Tokunosuke directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, 3600 Life Points vs. 2500!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.56,0:18:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tables have turned! I'll use my-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.44,0:18:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.44,0:18:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you gonna do an Exceed Summon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exceed Summon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot, he didn't notice this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.95,0:18:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma-kun, you can use my miss to your advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.26,0:18:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.26,0:18:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three level 1 Chuubone Juniors that got on your field because of my mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.50,0:18:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.73,0:18:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have three of the same level 1 monsters on my field!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! I can Exceed Summon, can't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.41,0:18:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a troublesome guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clearly, he is inviting Yuma to Exceed Summon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.79,0:18:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that card...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I overlay my three level 1 monsters, Chuubone Juniors!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.22,0:18:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't complete it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.55,0:19:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With these three monsters, I construct the Overlay network!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exceed Summon !!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.75,0:19:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out, Baby Tragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.40,0:19:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.48,0:19:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Exceed Summon was a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fell for it, Tsukumo Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.60,0:19:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,fell for it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.97,0:19:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my continuous trap card, Uratra C.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uratra C?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.19,0:19:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uratra C's effect- when Baby Tragon is successfully summoned to the opponent's field,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can choose one Exceed Monster from my opponent's extra deck,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.30,0:19:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special summon it to my side of the field, and equip this card to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:19:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From my extra deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.37,0:19:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, Aspiring Emperor - Hope now belongs to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll settle this right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment you Exceed Summoned Baby Tragon meant your luck coming to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of Exceed Summoning Baby Tragon,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.05,0:20:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He special summoned the 3 Chuubone Juniors to Yuma's side of the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.54,0:20:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.04,0:20:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, how did Tokunosuke know of my Baby Tragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote this for you with all my feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.53,0:20:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! The sender of that fan letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.30,0:20:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Tokunosuke!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.70,0:20:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the only thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.73,0:20:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who sent those fake photos to everyone's mobiles, just to make you all alone- that was also me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.10,0:20:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.37,0:20:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything has a flipside to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's sending you that fan letter,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.90,0:20:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or sending everyone those fake photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.01,0:20:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And of course, this duel included!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.49,0:20:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at the note on your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.84,0:20:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The note on my back...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.49,0:21:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you put this...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"In this duel, the winner will take from the loser one card of their liking, I have agreed."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ante-Rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.68,0:21:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokunosuke...!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I win, I will be taking your Aspiring Emperor - Hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Numbers..!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.94,0:21:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been deceiving me since the beginning, haven't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.86,0:21:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything you said about believing in me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.98,0:21:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or being my friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.82,0:21:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it all just a lie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.43,0:21:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This world is filled with hidden truths.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.15,0:21:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Falling for this is your own fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.18,0:21:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokunosuke--!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.36,0:21:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is human's hidden dark side..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.03,0:21:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the bizarre power's true form?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.52,0:21:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.49,0:21:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Continuous trap, Uratra C,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.54,0:21:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Activate !!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.36,0:21:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I special summon Aspiring Emperor Hope, from Yuma's extra deck!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.02,0:21:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And equipping it with this card.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.49,0:21:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Appear !!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.51,0:21:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aspiring Emperor, Hope !!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.78,0:22:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aspiring Emperor - Hope, it got stolen away..!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.03,0:22:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's duel! This week's question:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.10,0:22:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gogogo Golem's Attack Power is 1800. If it battles with Bugman Y which has 1400 Attack Power, what happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.15,0:22:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Today's test is hard. I can't divide myself from pleasure and temptation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.76,0:22:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wanna watch TV when I get home.\N The recent anime are fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.87,0:23:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In any case, this test is hard. \NLanguage, Math and English are especially bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.37,0:23:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm only average at science and social studies.\N The only thing I'm good at is P.E.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.55,0:23:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(Wait up, Baby!) For who's sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.25,0:23:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(Is that, Baby!) ...am I remembering...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.69,0:23:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(Just hold on, Baby!) ...the answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.25,0:23:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(What are we!? Baby!) ...they wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.92,0:23:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I write the correct answer on this paper,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.66,0:23:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in one year, in ten years, will anything change?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.40,0:23:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The world I drew in the corner of my dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.50,0:23:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}one day I will race through the open sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.28,0:23:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No one can blame this heart of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.15,0:23:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nothing is really correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.92,0:23:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokunosuke, why must you deceive everyone around you just to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.11,0:23:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Numbers cards, all of it will become mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.29,0:24:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Yu-Gi-Oh! ZeXal! "The Treacherous Numbers!?"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.65,0:24:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna bring it to 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.53,0:24:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gogogo Golem would destroy Bugman Y!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.40,0:24:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Afterwards, the 400 difference in Attack Power will become damage to your opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.56,0:24:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
